From 6a4c7068e1ef51e1d2119fb384c74bc771df2556 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 21:50:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add preset system, curated kicks, and WAV export (milestone
 8)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Preset system:
- src/presets.rs: 6 hand-tuned presets covering classic hardstyle, rawstyle
  screech, minimal tek, sub pressure, industrial stomp, and floating bounce.
- Preset strip in the UI (two rows of 3 buttons) above the parameter sections.
  Clicking a preset applies all parameters instantly via ParamSetter.

WAV export:
- src/render.rs: standalone renderer — instantiates fresh DSP objects, runs
  the full signal chain (crossover, oversampler, limiter) at 44.1 kHz, and
  writes a 32-bit float mono WAV via the hound crate.
- "Export WAV" button in the transport row; file lands at ~/hardkick-export.wav.

Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
